revisions.description: Update DESCRIPTION clause of MODULE-IDENTITY and PRODUCT-RELEASE clause of AGENT-CAPABILITIES.
Modified PRODUCT-RELEASE clause for consistent naming.
Added rbnIetfOspfCap2, updating to rfc4750 and adding support for objects previously not supported. Corrected spelling errors in DESCRIPTION clauses.

rbnIetfOspfCap.description: The Agent Capabilities of the implementation of the IETF OSPF-MIB. If this MIB implementation is platform-dependent, the PRODUCT-RELEASE clause contains Ericsson SEOS version and at least one of the following Ericsson product families: [SE] SmartEdge Multi-service Edge Router (MSER) family [SM] SM family of Metro Ethernet Service Transport platforms [SSR] Smart Service Router (SSR) family
